item.title: CVE-2023-3039|2024-08-02T06:41:04.167Z -- dell -- sd%20rom%20utility
item.description: SD ROM Utility, versions prior to 1.0.2.0 contain an Improper Access Control vulnerability. A low-privileged malicious user may potentially exploit this vulnerability to perform arbitrary code execution with limited access.
